{"tid":1948372,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連儂牆對呢班人呢講，幾乎係不可或缺嘅存在","createTime":"2020-03-29T03:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:52:32.000Z","uid":211994,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f23d4bdaca7f2c88c9bb44127e049e18d928f497","tid":1948372,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇見過以下嘅情景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvfFqcC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvfFqcC.jpg&h=fec4b666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場運動唔止年青人，中年同老年嘅手足都有參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地平時接收資訊嘅渠道就係屋企樓下嘅連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得有次銀髮手足搞大遊行，聽講就係靠連儂牆互相通報消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地如果只集中喺連登同tg傾我地嘅計劃同行動嘅話，呢一班手足就可以接收唔切，甚至係根本唔知我地將要做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決方法有三：<br />\n<br />\n1.落街貼文宣，如果要痴就要痴大張啲清晰啲，最好就係A4 size，資訊型文宣會比口號式文宣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.多啲同你身邊嘅叔叔姨姨公公婆婆分享下最近有咩活動，有咩資訊要知，當然幫佢地開個tg ac就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.唔好只係喺連登tg發播消息，多啲喺fb上分享文宣<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有咩睇法同建議呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊嚟傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咩話！？</span>你話唔知邊度有文宣可以攞嚟share？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣喇mention la app：<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/mention-la-文宣喇/id1488286618?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fmention-la-%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E5%96%87%2Fid1488286618%3Fl%3Den&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJexVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=95467c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/mention-la-文宣喇/id1488286618?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣tg channel，咁多個月一直都有更新㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HK_Schedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_Schedule&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJexVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=124e1821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_Schedule</a>"},{"pid":"3df6eb652b96f6c137bf3ca3e094a2be55f4b407","tid":1948372,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8059b5786caf2187bd42027d41b61466b4939c76","tid":1948372,"uid":133806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"好多上咗年紀嘅都會企喺連儂牆睇下啲內容好<br />\n無論佢哋點諗都好，俾到班阿伯阿婆知道下我哋諗乜嘢係有好處<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係啲藍shit點會成日做獅子狗丫"},{"pid":"f7f74ca9da70307ba2bbb8f329ecdcb085b272c9","tid":1948372,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8408cbfaca2bee50ff673ea85b4583d36a1c52f0","tid":1948372,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"圖書館戰爭其實可以參考下"},{"pid":"55975ce1a0da015ad3bec42a918d67f4ca2c07e1","tid":1948372,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"其實真係有唔少人行過會睇"},{"pid":"9eefd8d9f68eb0f7d408b583307c8af7a35d4a68","tid":1948372,"uid":117636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"授人以魚，不如授之以漁啦<br />\n連儂牆宜家風險高左咁多，又快俾人拆<br />\n如果佢地真係會攞筆抄低，咁不如整啲文宣教佢地用TG<br />\n區議會搞啲用電話同TG班，禮義廉以前都有智能電話班<br />\n長遠黎講好過用俾狗咬，俾人打黎換啲唔識用電話既人睇"},{"pid":"450f42db5a082f7793d79d5576eaec2eeb50a444","tid":1948372,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\